description:
Timothy was probably Paul's favorite of his many assistants. In this episode, Apollos, another of Paul's protoges, explains the contents of the letter written to Timothy known as First Timothy.

Scripture
1 Timothy

Director: Phil Smith
Stars: Tim Urban
